2007-07-24  Rémi Humbert  <humbert@gostai.com>

	Some changes to the API, some crypto functions added (RSA, AES).
	* crypt.cc: New.
	* crypt.hh: New: Inherit Crypto, defines two functions, crypt and
	decrypt. It should be used as a base class for crypting algorithms.

	* cryptaes.cc: New.
	* cryptaes.hh: New: Inherit Crypt. Implement the decrypt function
	which use the AES algorithm and a key and iv. The crypt function
	has to be done.

	* crypto.cc: New.
	* crypto.hh: New. This class is the main cryptography class that is
	the base class for Sign and Crypt class. It contains functions to
	set the in and out streams (the streams processed by the cryptographic
	algorithms) and to set the private/public keys used in the algorithms.

	* cryptrsa.cc: New.
	* cryptrsa.hh: New: Inherit Crypt. Implement the decrypt function
	which use the RSA algorithm and a private key. The crypt function
	has to be done.

	* sign.cc: .
	* sign.hh: Remove the message/signature setting functions. Add the
	check function that was in the Verify class.

	* signsha1.hh: Remove the implementation of the functions and put them
	in a separate file.
	* signsha1.cc: New: contains the implementation of the functions that
	where in the associated .hh. Added also is the implementation of the
	'check' function, that was previously in the VerifySHA1 class.

	* utility.hh: New.
	* utility.cc: New: Contains the implementation of the file loading
	functions, plus some usefull functions. All functions are declared
	static.

	* verify.cc: Remove.
	* verify.hh: Remove. Features of this class have be displaced in the
	Sign class (sign.{hh,cc} files).

	* verifysha1.hh: Remove. Features of this class have be displaced in
	the SignSHA1 class (signsha1.{hh,cc} files).

	* debug-log.cc: Change header to GOSTAI new one.
	* debug-log.hh: Change header to GOSTAI new one.

	* exception.hh: Change header to GOSTAI new one. Add a macro.

	* openssl.cc: Change header to GOSTAI new one.
	* openssl.hh: Change header to GOSTAI new one.

	* urbi-crypto.mk: Add the new files in the compilation, remove deleted
	ones.

	* tests/Makefile.am: .
	* tests/sign.cc: Use the new API, the principle of the test stays
	the same.
	* tests/verify.cc: Use the new API, the principle of the test stays
	the same.

